snippet.title: The Dark Eye: Book of Heroes -- how to make your own hero!
snippet.description:
In the upcoming new Coop-RPG "The Dark Eye: Book of Heroes", you can pick from 4 species and 12 professions. Chose your character wisely!
Put it on your wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1139870/The_Dark_Eye__Book_of_Heroes/
